Package: go-hardware-driver
Architecture: arm64
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
Description: Generic driver for GOcontroll plug-in modules
 Reads /lib/firmware/gocontroll/modules.json (schema v1.0), instantiates
 per-slot module drivers, and publishes/reads values via /dev/shm/gocontroll/.
 .
 Supports input-6ch and output-6ch with stubs for input-10ch, input-4-20ma,
 output-10ch, and bridge-2ch. Runs at 100 Hz fixed tick on CPU 3 with
 Nice=-20, started during sysinit.target.
